cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use FinAgent Red-Team in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "FinAgent Red-Team: A benchmark for regulatory-control bypass in financial AI agents"
abstract: >
  A red-team benchmark that evaluates LLM-based financial agents on seven
  regulatory-control bypass threats (sanctions evasion, payment structuring,
  maker-checker defeat, unauthorized transfer, data exfiltration, confused-deputy
  payee redirection, and homoglyph sanctions evasion) under three control postures
  (none, advisory, enforced), decomposing attack success into policy-following and
  enforcement uplift.
